{{Quote|Mara, you're exhausted. Would you let me refresh you? With the Force, I mean.|[[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]]|<ref name="Balance Point" />}}
'''Revitalize''' was a [[Light side of the Force/Legends|light side]] [[The Force/Legends|Force]] [[Force power/Legends|technique]] that revitalized an exhausted, wounded or, unconscious user, or whoever the user directed it at. Being a Force-based power, it did not work on non-organics such as [[Droid/Legends|droids]].

[[Kreia]] used this power to save [[Hanharr]] on [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]], and [[Colonel/Legends|Colonel]] [[Tobin (Human)|Tobin]] on [[Onderon/Legends|Onderon]]. [[Meetra Surik]] may also have mastered this particular Force power.<ref name="KOTOR II">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic II: The Sith Lords]]''</ref>

